//
//! # Long-Term Support Framework
//!
//! Release lifecycle management:
//!
//! - **LTS Versions**: Even minor versions (1.0, 1.2, 2.0) receive extended support
//! - **3-Year Lifecycle**: 18 months active + 12 months maintenance + 6 months security
//! - **Security Backports**: Critical patches backported to all supported versions
//! - **Deprecation Notices**: 6-month advance warning before end-of-life
//!
//! ## Version Naming
//!
//! ```text
//! MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH
//!   │     │     └── Bug fixes (no breaking changes)
//!   │     └──────── Features (even = LTS, odd = standard)
//!   └────────────── Breaking changes
//! ```
//!
//! ## Support Timeline
//!
//! ```text
//! ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
//! │ ACTIVE (18 mo)  │ MAINTENANCE (12 mo) │ SECURITY (6 mo) │
//! │ Features + Bugs │ Bugs + Security     │ Security Only   │
//! └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
//!                                                     ▲
//!                                                    EOL
//! ```

